import React from 'react' import "./Tests.css" {/*
GENERAL QUESTIONNAIRE
  • Self-Rated Level 1 Cross-Cutting Symptom Measure
    Take a quick tour to the DSM Questionnaire to discover your current mental health condition.
SPECIALIZED TESTSs
  • Autism Tests
    Are you experiencing the most common symptoms of autism? Find out using our Autism tests.
  • Depression Tests
    Are you depressed for any recent happenings aroung you? Take some moment to go through our Depression tests.
  • OCD Tests
    Suffering from obsessive thoughts of compulsive behavior? Take a tour to our OCD tests.
  • Orthorexia Tests
    Having eating disorders in a healthy way? Find out using our Orthorexia tests.
  • PTSD Tests
    Any horrible course of events that are still terrifying you? Find out through our PTSD tests.
  • Stress Tests
    Too much stressed? Take a tour to our Stress diagnosis process.
*/} const Tests = ({tests}) => { return (
General Questionnaire
Self-Rated Level 1 Cross-Cutting Symptom Measure
Are you experiencing the most common symptoms of autism? Find out using our Autism tests.
